<!-- table:view -->
<table class="view" summary="ABOUT MOHW &gt; Press Release detail.">
<caption>ABOUT MOHW &gt; Press Release</caption>
<colgroup>
<col width="12%"/><col width="38%"/><col width="12%"/><col width="38%"/>
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Subject</th>
<td colspan="3">Customized service for persons with developmental disabilities will be provided</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Date</th>
<td>2012-07-13</td>
<th scope="row">Hit</th>
<td>5024</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">Contents</th>
<td class="view" colspan="3"><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><u><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 12pt"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Customized service for persons with developmental disabilities will be provided<o:p></o:p></font></font></span></u></b></p>
<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾çÁß°íµñ','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ">- </font></span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Establishment of a comprehensive support plan specialized by disability type for those with developmental disabilities -</font></span></font></font></p>
<div align="center">
<table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="MsoNormalTable" style="border-bottom: medium none; border-left: medium none; border-collapse: collapse; border-top: medium none; border-right: medium none; mso-border-alt: solid black .25pt; mso-table-overlap: never; mso-yfti-tbllook: 1184">
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 92.05pt; mso-yfti-irow: 0; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes">
<td style="border-bottom: black 1pt solid; border-left: black 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 1.4pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 5.1pt; width: 473.4pt; padding-right: 5.1pt; height: 92.05pt; border-top: black 1pt solid; border-right: black 1pt solid; padding-top: 1.4pt; mso-border-alt: solid black .25pt" width="631">
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ms mincho'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'ms mincho'">❍</span><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"> </span><span lang="EN-US">(Protection of right) Training course and work manual for adult guardians will be prepared and activities expenses will be provided </span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ms mincho'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'ms mincho'">❍</span><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"> </span><span lang="EN-US">(Diagnosis and treatment) Early diagnosis and treatment system for developmental disabilities will be established and the voucher support will be expanded </span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ms mincho'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'ms mincho'">❍</span><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"> </span><span lang="EN-US">(Caring support) The service to support disabled people’s activities will be expanded and parents counseling and information will be provided </span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ms mincho'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'ms mincho'">❍</span><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"> </span><span lang="EN-US">(Health and income support) The health insurance will be applied to dental treatment anesthesia and the secured employment will be expanded. The release of a pension and trust products for income guarantee will be promoted.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></span></font></font></font></p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
	 </p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US">The government announced that it finalized the “Support Plan for Persons with Developmental Disabilities” by convening the national policy coordinating meeting (presided by Prime Minister) on 6 Jul. (Fri.). </span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Developmental disabilities refer to disabilities with lack of intelligent capabilities and communication abilities such as mental retardation and autistic disorder. </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US">There are currently 183 thousand persons with developmental disabilities registered. (as of Dec. 2011) </span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Many of them have severe disabilities that require special care and protection for their entire lives just like the main characters in movies such as </font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶','serif'; mso-ascii-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ">“</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Barefoot Gi Bong,</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶','serif'; mso-ascii-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ">”</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"> </font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶','serif'; mso-ascii-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ">“</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Marathon,</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶','serif'; mso-ascii-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ">”</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"> and </font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶','serif'; mso-ascii-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ">“</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Rain Man.</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶','serif'; mso-ascii-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ">”</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"> </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">However, the protection system and support for those with developmental disabilities that </font></span></font></font><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">need special social care fall far short of the demand.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -4.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 4.6pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US">Therefore, those with developmental disabilities that don’t have ability to protect themselves can easily fall victim to abuse, sexual violence and human trafficking.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: -0.4pt; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">They suffer great deals of discrimination when using casual facilities such as restaurants and hospitals. </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US">It is known that developmental disabilities can be greatly eased especially in terms of speaking ability and behavior disorder when treated at an early phase. </span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">However, due to lack of trustworthy diagnostic tools and experts as well as parents’ tendency of not willing to admit their children’s problems, actual early intervention is being delayed.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾çÁß°íµñ','serif'; letter-spacing: 0.2pt"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ">*</font></span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">The test is repeated by 3.8 times on an average (7.8 times in the case of autistic disorder) because the result of the test on developmental disabilities cannot be trusted and thus, 1.04 million won (average) is spent.</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾çÁß°íµñ','serif'; letter-spacing: 0.2pt"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ"> </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
	 </p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">In the meantime, parents who acknowledged their children’s disabilities are spending considerable amounts of money for treatment but are having great difficulty due to lack of trustworthy treatment institutions and information.</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'hci poppy','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ"> </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">People with severe developmental disabilities who cannot handle basic daily routines such as face washing, dressing, and bathroom use even after they are fully grown up are being mostly taken care of by their parents. </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾çÁß°íµñ','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ">* </font></span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Those who can do every basic daily activity take up just 10.2% of the entire number of people with developmental disabilities</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾çÁß°íµñ','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ"> </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Many parents give up their jobs or leisure time as they take care of their disabled children and even when their own parents pass away or their brother or sister get married, they mostly cannot attend funerals or weddings. </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -5.2pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 5.2pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾çÁß°íµñ','serif'; letter-spacing: 0.2pt"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ">* </font></span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Those who cannot attend family gatherings such as parent’s funeral or sibling’s wedding because of their children’s developmental disabilities 42.7%</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾çÁß°íµñ','serif'; letter-spacing: 0.2pt"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ"> </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Due to this situation, many guardians (52%) are emotionally suffering almost to the point of depression and some of them face the crisis of seeing their families being torn apart such as divorce because of the matter of taking care of their disabled children. (Those who have experienced separation or divorce; 7.1%)</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'hci poppy','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ"> </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">The Support Plan for Persons with Developmental Disabilities announced this time, </font></span></b></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -4.7pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 4.7pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US">holds great significance as it is a customized support plan that is specified by disability type, moving away from just having a basic framework such as employment promotion, special education, discrimination prohibition and the pension for the disabled and the introduction of the activity support system for all the disabled.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">The government said that it is expecting to see the situations of those with developmental disabilities and their families eventually get better as support policies will be continuously carried out based on this plan.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">First of all, the right protection system will be established such as early settlement of adult guardians* that will be in charge of protecting adults with developmental disabilities and regular search and inspection of islands, salt fields and ship to eradicate human trafficking. </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 8pt; mso-char-indent-count: -1.0">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'ÇÑ¾çÁß°íµñ','serif'; letter-spacing: -1pt"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ">* </font></span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Adult guardians are the ones that help with money management, medical activities and residence decision those with developmental disabilities that have difficulty in making decisions</font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">In preparation for the implementation of the adult guardianship system (1 Jul. 2013), the implementation system is being prepared, adult guardians will be nurtured and their activity expense support is planned. </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Ministry of Health and Welfare, National Police Agency and Korea Coast Guard will work together to eradicate abduction and human trafficking through regular inspection of vulnerable areas more than twice a year.</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'hci poppy','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ"> </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Second, the diagnosis and treatment system will be established for early intervention in developmental disabilities and appropriate treatment and the voucher support will be expanded. </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2">Precise examination tool (including Balley-III) will be developed for infants who are suspected of having developmental disabilities as a result of K-ASQ which is conducted for all infants now and the exam cost support will be expanded by phase. </font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -10pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: -1.0">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">In addition, through restricting, Seoul National Hospital will be responsible for core functions of research and survey related to developmental disabilities and behavioral treatment rooms (self-injury and attack) will be set up by phase starting with National Seoul Hospital.</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'hci poppy','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ"> </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">The subjects of the developmental disability rehabilitation service voucher which is provided to households with income that is below 100% of the national average household income (4,387 thousand won a month for a four-member family) will be gradually expanded. </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2">District rehabilitation hospitals will be playing a major hospital in charge of overall rehabilitation treatment in the concerned area in the long-term (6 district rehabilitation hospitals: Incheon, Busan, Kangwon, Gwangju, Daejeon and Jeju) </font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US">Thirdly, to ease the burden on families of those with developmental disabilities, the support service for activities of the disabled will be expanded and counseling and information for parents will be provided.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"> </span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2">The activity support service now only 1<sup>st</sup> grade disabled people can apply for will become available for 2<sup>nd</sup> grade disabled people and the amount of support for children which has been only a half of that for adults (42~62 hours) will be also increased. </font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">The care service for severely disabled children will be expanded as the cost paid by each individual will be differentiated and the maximum service hours per year will be expanded.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Manuals will be distributed and the support centers for disabled children and those with developmental disabilities will be set up and operated to provide information to parents regarding how to protect their children with developmental disabilities. (Aug.)</font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -4.6pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 4.6pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">The psychological counseling support for parents of children with developmental disabilities who are suspected of having depression will be carried out in Seoul (the service will be provided in Aug.) and then be expanded throughout the nation..</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'hci poppy','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ"> </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US">The application of the health insurance fee to the cost of general anesthesia when those with developmental disabilities receive the treatment for dental caries, the expansion of secured employment, and the release of a pension and trust products to guarantee supplemental incomes will be promoted.</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: -0.4pt; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: ÇÑ¾ç½Å¸íÁ¶"> </span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 5pt; mso-char-indent-count: -.5">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">The application of the health insurance will be promoted to reduce additional cost burden for general anesthesia that those with developmental disabilities need when receiving dental treatment as they cannot control their moves according to doctors’ instructions.</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'hci poppy','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ"> </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: -10pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 10pt; mso-char-indent-count: -1.0">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">In addition, jobs appropriate for persons with developmental disabilities will be developed and types of work at protective working facilities for the disabled that are mostly tall-processing will be diversified to agricultural and service areas.</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 'hci poppy','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: ÈÞ¸Õ¸íÁ¶; mso-hansi-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin"><font face="¹ÙÅÁ"> </font></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">Also, the pension product considering characteristics of those with developmental disabilities will be released and the trust products for the disabled that cannot actually be accessed by those with developmental disabilities will be improved.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span></font></font></font></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ"><span lang="EN-US">Prime Minister (Kim, Hwang Sik) said, “those with developmental disabilities are the most vulnerable people in our society that needs the nation’s special attention and support” at the national policy coordinating meeting that finalized the support plan for persons with developmental disabilities. </span></font></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="¸¼Àº °íµñ" size="2"> </font></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt">
<font size="2"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="¸¼Àº °íµñ">He urged, “I ask each ministry to continuously carry out measures so that the support plan for persons with developmental disabilities will be well executed.” </font></span></font></font></p></td>
</tr>
